name: The Surreal Sunset
description: The sky turned blue, then yellow, then red, as I was about to drift off to bed. I grabbed the camera and took the shot, then ran off to process to see what I got. I gazed in amazement at what I found, at all the colors that abound. So this surreal sunset I make available to you, that joy may spread to others too. @fotochad (An animated photo of a surreal sunset in California.)
